# Supabase Realtime

## Golden Rule

**Always use Supabase Realtime** instead of custom WebSocket implementations.

- ✅ Built-in authentication (uses Supabase Auth tokens)
- ✅ RLS enforcement (respects DB security policies)
- ✅ Scales with Supabase infra (no custom servers)
- ✅ Type-safe (with generated types)
- ❌ Do NOT implement custom WebSockets for data sync.
